Note that when first opening these references and using &#x2013;profile=word, they are not formatted yet and only appear as numbers. To change the citation style, go to the references tab and then change the style in the style selector. Standard LaTeX References have the style IEEE 2006. <br/>Note that the bibliography is not added by default if you used &#x2013;profile=word . In this case you again go to the references tab, click on Bibliography and then on Works cited to insert it yourself.</p>
